raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Suzanna: Hello everyone 😥
Suzanna: I'm looking for a sub-in for a little emergency
Mabel: Oh no! What's the problem Professor!?
Suzanna: I can't disclose the details unfortunately but I'm in need of one of the boys here
Suzanna: Caleb said he would but he has a schedule conflict on Saturday
Naomi: Right 😅 I'm sorry about that Suzanna
Naomi: I'd have someone else volunteer but ours is a sensitive topic as well 😅
Suzanna: That's fine Naomi, I'm not faulting you for this
Mabel: Babe, do you think you can help them? 🥺
- [Help Suzanna] [#orangeheart]
	set Story.orange_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"Suzanna1\"
	Player: Sure
	Player: What can I do for you Suzanna?
	Suzanna: My hero 🥹
	Suzanna: Okay I have some preparations to make tonight but I'll let you know first thing in the morning
	Suzanna: Please keep Saturday free
	Player: Okay! 😅
	Mabel: Babe you're a hero!
	Player: Am I? 😆
- [Help Naomi] [#redheart]
	set Story.red_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"Naomi1\"
	Player: Is there any way I can help you Naomi?
	Player: Maybe Caleb can help Suzanna then
	Naomi: Actually... 🤔
	Naomi: You can
	Naomi: I'll have to chit chat about it with Caleb tonight then tomorrow we can talk about it
	Player: Sure 🫡
	Naomi: Thanks!
	Naomi: I'll make sure Caleb's free for Sat then Prof
	Suzanna: Oh that's great to hear 🥹
	Suzanna: I'll have to make some preparations then, thanks again
	Naomi: No worries!
	Mabel: Babe, you're a hero!
	Player: Am I? 😆
- [Help Neither]
	set Story.flag = \"Nobody2\"
	Player: I've got some plans for Saturday so sorry about that 😅
	Suzanna: That's quite unlucky for me then 😓
	Suzanna: Alright, thank you anyway
Suzanna: Gotta run, thanks everyone
Mabel: Hope it goes well!
Mabel: I wonder what she's struggling with
Naomi: Suzanna's got some unique situations on her hands
Naomi: 😅
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
